Subject: [PATCH] ARM: configs: Add bytedevkit fragment
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

Add necessary configs to use all features from byteDEVKIT.

Signed-off-by: Alexander Forsch <alexander.forsch@bytesatwork.ch>
Signed-off-by: Oliver St√§bler <oliver.staebler@bytesatwork.ch>
Signed-off-by: Daniel Ammann <daniel.ammann@bytesatwork.ch>
---
 MAINTAINERS                                   |  1 +
 .../configs/fragment-901-bytedevkit.config    | 19 +++++++++++++++++++
 2 files changed, 20 insertions(+)
 create mode 100644 arch/arm/configs/fragment-901-bytedevkit.config

diff --git a/MAINTAINERS b/MAINTAINERS
index 169080b2e3cb..f9a955dcba54 100644
--- a/MAINTAINERS
+++ b/MAINTAINERS
@@ -4503,6 +4503,7 @@ M:	Daniel Ammann <daniel.ammann@bytesatwork.ch>
 S:	Maintained
 F:	.github/workflows/checkpatch.yml
 F:	Documentation/devicetree/bindings/arm/bytesatwork/bytesatwork.yaml
+F:	arch/arm/configs/fragment-901-bytedevkit.config
 F:	drivers/gpu/drm/panel/panel-youritec-ili9806e.c
 F:	drivers/video/logo/logo_baw_clut224.ppm
 
diff --git a/arch/arm/configs/fragment-901-bytedevkit.config b/arch/arm/configs/fragment-901-bytedevkit.config
new file mode 100644
index 000000000000..602321a70295
--- /dev/null
+++ b/arch/arm/configs/fragment-901-bytedevkit.config
@@ -0,0 +1,19 @@
+CONFIG_DRM_PANEL_YOURITECH_ILI9806E=y
+
+CONFIG_LOGO=y
+# CONFIG_LOGO_LINUX_MONO is not set
+# CONFIG_LOGO_LINUX_VGA16 is not set
+# CONFIG_LOGO_LINUX_CLUT224 is not set
+CONFIG_LOGO_BAW_CLUT224=y
+
+CONFIG_DRM_FBDEV_EMULATION=y
+
+CONFIG_DP83867_PHY=y
+
+CONFIG_MFD_STM32_TIMERS=y
+CONFIG_PWM_STM32=y
+
+CONFIG_FRAMEBUFFER_CONSOLE=y
+CONFIG_FRAMEBUFFER_CONSOLE_DETECT_PRIMARY=y
+# CONFIG_FRAMEBUFFER_CONSOLE_ROTATION is not set
+# CONFIG_FRAMEBUFFER_CONSOLE_DEFERRED_TAKEOVER is not set
